// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2362 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 9a82e99a-62ac-54c8-98dd-043d18d8af41

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:5* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:6* OR ImageFileName = *redhat/ubi9:*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
